text: Beautifully maintained 1-1/2 Story Home in awesome 55+ Montreaux Community! The open floor is great for entertaining w/Kitchen open to Dining & Living Rm w/gas fireplace. 3 Bedrooms incl the Huge Primary `en suite & Study/Office (or 4th bed) on Main Level w/2 Guest Rms, huge Bonus/Hobby Room & full Bath on Upper Level. Kitchen cabinets are bright white & you have tons of storage +great prep surfaces on slab granite counters. New LVP flooring runs through Kitchen & Dining spaces. The home has added perks including EV charging station in the garage, a Hot Tub & upgraded landscaping in the beautiful back yard/patio area + AC for those hotter Summer days! 25 new Solar Panels will provide you cost savings & energy efficiency as well!

Tri-Level home located on an oversized corner lot in the desirable Thunderbird neighborhood. Sit outside underneath the front covered porch with your morning coffee or hang out on the large back deck enjoying wildlife and nature. The back yard is fully fenced with plenty of room for boat or RV parking. The main floor features living room with fireplace, dining room and kitchen. The real bonus is the half finished basement with living space, a couple of rooms, laundry room and half bath. This is an opportunity to become a home owner today and gain some sweat equity with some cosmetic work. Large garden shed is perfect for extra storage along with the attached 2 car garage. Come see this today.

Beautiful 2 story home in Blackburn Ridge offers shy 1600 sq ft, 3 BR's & 2 1/2 baths. Nicely remodeled main living area recently w/ new flooring and quartz countertops. Open floor plan w/ Nat gas Fireplace in living room, bay window w/ seating & storage under. Kitchen w/ eating bar, walk-in pantry, Kitchen aid flat top range w/ downdraft, office area off the kitchen, near laundry room. Double doors to private back tile patio w/ cement curbing. Nice water feature in back also. Fully fenced yard. All 3 BR's are upstairs, primary w/ double vanity, tile floor & spacious tile shower. Attached 2 car garage, Hardy Plank siding, new composition roof recently. Well-maintained home on a cul-de-sac w/ westerly views in a very desirable area.

Welcome to this 3-bedroom 2 bath home waiting for your design inspirations. The living room, kitchen, & dining rooms flow together on the main level. Kitchen has ample storage and looks at to the large backyard. The bedrooms are upstairs. Master bedroom is spacious overlooking the big backyard. Lower level has the family room, laundry, & bath. Access the covered patio & huge private backyard from the family room. Home has a 2-car garage & plenty of room for RV's & toy parking. Gas forced air furnace, gas fireplace & air conditioning to keep you cool in the summer. This property may qualify for Seller Financing (Vendee). Sold As-Is. Buyer to verify all information.

There are stunning views of Similk Bay and the surrounding islands from almost every room of this wonderful home. The main level is 2792 SF with 3 bedrooms, 2.25 bathrooms. The great room has a living room with fireplace and access to a large deck for entertaining. The great room also includes a formal dining area. The kitchen has lots of cabinets, island and pantry, informal dining area. The family room also has a fireplace and is a cozy space to read. Office/ Den. Master bedroom with deck access, walk in closets and master bath with two separate sinks. Lower level is 1400 SF unfinished space with large windows and views. A newer boiler system is on the lower level that keeps all the baseboard radiators warm.

New construction single level home by Landed Gentry of our Warner floor plan. This beautiful floor plan is 1, 368 sf. Featuring 2 bedrooms, study/bedroom and 1.75 bath. The central living area includes vaulted ceiling and expansive luxury vinyl plank throughout the entry/living/kitchen/dining areas/laundry. Finishes include stained cabinetry, granite counters, tile accents and ss appliances. Home will be fully landscaped with fenced rear yard on quite dead end street. The home is also a 2 minute drive to local restaurants & grocery stores and 8 minute drive to riverfront park. Move in ready!

Cottage home in Shelter Bay. Spacious living room with vaulted cedar ceilings, skylights, and propane stove. Updated kitchen has a lot of counters, storage and newer appliances. Formal entry with parquet floors and plenty of closet space. Primary Bedroom is in rear of house for optimum privacy, and includes a bath and his & her closets. Greenbelt next to side yard. Newer Roof. Single car garage + a workshop + a storage shed! Light and bright with brand new carpet, all main floor living what's not to love?

Amazing Skagit County home near golf course and airport with easy I-5 access. Beautiful 2, 775 sf home with open floor plan and thoughtful upgrades is ready for you. Main level living room, family room, dining room, laundry w/ bath, kitchen with bkfst nook, pantry and stainless appliances. Luxurious primary suite with fireplace and bath with heated floors. French doors lead to covered deck for outdoor living. Upstairs features loft area perfect for exercise/office, 2 bdrms, full bath with heated floors, and guest suite with bath. New HVAC, tankless water heater and ductless heat/ac in bdrms make this home comfortable year round. Fenced backyard with playhouse and large shed, and 2 car garage complete this fantastic home. Dont miss it!

Welcome home to this affordable move in ready home! with a little TLC make this your forever home.Mud room , This home has 2 bedrooms 2 bath & large partially fenced yard just waiting to put your final touches to make it yours. Deck on back for entertaining or just enjoying those summer days. Utility room of kitchen, dinning area in kitchen. Plenty of parking space for your RV, snowmobiles, boats or ?. 2 small storage sheds and a concrete slab.

Spacious Rambler on a beautiful, flat one acre lot, Space for RV / Boat Parking or add a shop. 3 Car Garage. Neighborhood is gated for added security and privacy and is adjacent to Rasar State Park which has great access to the Skagit River and extensive walking trails. The home is completed with maple cabinets, LVP floors, slab granite counters, full height backsplash, white painted millwork, wood wrapped windows, double panel white painted doors and stainless steel appliances. Vaulted ceilings in the huge family room, dining room and a huge master bedroom make this home extremely functional. Hybrid heat pump water heater, High Efficiency ductless mini splits provide both heating and air conditioning to the entire living area.

This is your chance to own a large unit in the desirable Bayview Mobile Park. Views out your windows & from the deck to Padilla Bay & across to Anacortes. This 3 bedroom 2 bath home has ample living space with open concept. Plenty of storage in walk in hall closet. Spacious, bright kitchen, two living rooms & dining area to entertain. Serenity awaits in your park like landscaped lot with large front lawn. Covered parking under carport as well as large storage shed with loft for extra storage space. Handicap accessible ramps at rear of home. Heat pump with A/C. Padilla Bay Walking Trail just below 55+ Age restriction

Nestled in the heart of the PNW's picturesque landscape, this stunning home offers a peaceful escape surrounded by nature's beauty. Relax & entertain effortlessly on one of two charming patios, where the bay breeze creates a perfect atmosphere. Inside, find 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, & a fully remodeled kitchen w/ butcher block counters, ample storage & SS appliances. Enjoy the rustic charm of the exposed beams, sourced from the property. Large windows adorn the living space, framing a year-round picturesque view of Skagit Bay & Martha's Beach. Situated on a spacious 14, 233 sq ft lot, the property boasts lush landscaping & utmost privacy. Enjoy private beach access -high bank. Make sure to check out all of the community amenities available.

Charming craftsman rambler, on 1.0 level acre, in an unbeatable location! Minutes from I-5 + Downtown MV, bordered by farmland on the north & the Tulip Winery on the west. This rambler is the perfect balance of the old farmhouse feel with modern upgrades. Front door opens to sizeable Great Room with recently refinished original hardwood floors & new windows. Great Room leads to updated kitchen with new: flooring, cabinets, countertop & sink. Kitchen features ample storage space & original built-ins. Primary bedroom features walk-in closet & connects with fully updated full bath. Secondary bedroom also connects with updated full bath & also features a walk-in closet. Third bedroom features newer flooring and connects with utility room.

Peaceful country living that is only 19 minutes from Sedro Woolley!!! Don't miss your chance to buy this nicely updated, 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, move in ready, 1, 512 square foot home that is sitting on a 1.16 acre lot! A large 36'x24' shop gives plenty of space for extra storage, and outdoor toys! Newly installed bamboo flooring throughout the main living space, with freshly painted walls and trim. Gorgeous, newly installed butcher block counter tops, new dishwasher, and microwave. This is a prime location for the outdoor enthusiast with fishing, camping, and hiking trails near by! Or if you prefer the comforts of home, then you have plenty of room for gardening, and landscaping to create your very own at home oasis!!!

Immerse yourself in this beautiful modern home located in the Whistle Ridge neighborhood. As you enter, you will find style in the open concept floorplan, featuring high ceilings, a stone fireplace, chef's kitchen complete w/granite countertops and SS appliances. A large bath w/ a walk-in, tiled shower, & bedroom on the main level make this home perfect for having guests. The patio off the kitchen provides access to a fully fenced backyard & the oversized 2 car garage allows for parking & storage. Upstairs you will find the primary suite w/distant views of mountains & Fidalgo Bay, walk-in closet & large bath w/ DBL sinks. 2 additional bedrooms, lg bonus room, full bath, & lg laundry room with sink & cabinets complete this beautiful home.

text: PRICE REDUCED! Beautifully maintained home in the heart of Burlington within walking distance to parks, shopping restaurants and more. This 2 bedroom 1 bath home has some wonderful features such as office space in primary bedroom and a large laundry/mud room with deep sink and storage. Attached 2 car garage in back of the house and off street parking. This house is zoned MR-NB. The MR-NB zone allows for a mix of residential and non-residential uses. Permitted non-residential uses include contractor offices, light industrial, personal services, and professional offices. Other uses, such as small (less than 1, 000 square feet) eating and drinking establishments, and commercial daycares may be allowed with a conditional use permit.

Welcome to Sauk Mountain Estates! As you step inside this charming home, you'll immediately notice the updated vinyl flooring and the large windows that let the natural light pour in. Upstairs you'll find 3 spacious bedrooms with new carpet and 2 full bathrooms. The fully fenced backyard and patio provide a peaceful retreat ideal for entertaining guests, gardening or just simply relaxing. All appliances stay. New roof 5 months old - 25 yr transferable warranty. AC and Generator included - with transferable service contract. Stick built shed in the back yard for storage. This home is move-in ready!

Clean maintained used for camping purposes.Plenty of trees, raw natural land to give feeling of the beauty in the Cascade Mountains. Power, water available in street.Soil test will need to be done to install septic. Roll in a Cabin or RV right away & start nesting here at your own property. Check with county & make your next building plans permitted here. Minutes away from community boat launch for outdoor activities fishing, birds, elk & tons of wildlife to site see. Check out Mt. Baker for skiing. Nearest amenities 5 minutes away.

Welcome to 705 Warner Street in the heart of Sedro-Woolley. This charming single-family home comes with a large detached garageperfect for storing your toys, tools, or creating a workshop space. The spacious yard provides ample room for outdoor activities, gardening, and relaxation. Imagine enjoying sunny afternoons in your yard or tinkering away in the detached garage. The property truly offers a delightful blend of indoor and outdoor living. All this and only minutes from downtown and I-5.

It's unusual to find a one level, high performance, healthy, home that is designed with both entertaining and aging-in-place features. This stunning home looks out onto the natural beauty of the surrounding hills and Clear Lake. The landscape incorporates both NW forest features and specialty plants. It invites you to come outside. Built by nationally recognized Martha Rose Construction, it has all of the features typical of the homes she builds. Find out what it's like to live with low utility bills and fresh indoor air due to a large solar array on the roof and a heat recovery ventilation system. Low maintenance building materials abound and make it a breeze to live here. Everything has been considered for its impact on the environment.

Step into this mid-century charmer in the heart of Old Town and be greeted by its timeless allure. Centrally located, it offers easy access to downtown parks, lifestyle amenities, library, theater, restaurants and schools. Inside, the home exudes mid-century vibes with hardwood floors and central fireplace, complemented by a distinctive wood ceiling detail and accent wall. Boasting 2 bedrooms, 1 full bath and long single-car garage, it also features a generous laundry/mud room leading to the backyard. A quaint patio area, accessed from the kitchen slider, beckons for outdoor gatherings. Surrounded by mature trees, this home brims with potential for your dream retreat. Don't miss the chance to add your personal touch to this sweet home!

text: Beautiful Cabin like home on 5 acres tucked away at the base of Sauk mountain. Stunning almost lake size pond that is fed by 2 year round creeks & features a dock/walking trail around pond or just to sit back and enjoy from the comfort of your covered country front porch. Enjoy all the beauty of the old growth trees on the property, walking trails, fruit trees, berries and even a walnut tree. Live off grid, live organically, bring your goats & chickens or turn this hidden gem into an Airbnb for future investment. This home needs some TLC to bring it back to its glory but the picture perfect scenery and possibilities are what should motivate you to make this your next home a home away from home, Air BNB /investment property. Sold AS IS.

Fabulous main level living in Old Town with lots of potential. This ideally located home is in the Historic Old Town neighborhood of Anacortes. Desirable main level living with additional room in the basement await your imagination and finishing touches. Beautiful yard filters sunlight through the windows and the detached garage provides additional opportunities and room to expand. Two current main level bedrooms in addition to an office/utility room. Utility room could be moved back to basement with office potential to convert to a third bedroom on the main. Basement is full of potential as well.

30' moorage slip located in Skyline Marina, just minutes from downtown Anacortes. Skyline Marina is the gateway to San Juan Islands, with the shortest run into the islands of any marina. Skyline is a full service marina with fuel, chandlery, repair, dry storage, and hoist/launch facilities, yacht club. You will find: restrooms, showers, laundry facilities, groceries and ice, garbage receptacles, ample parking. Slip is 30' in length and 14.9' wide. Adjoining slip is also for sale, together they're 29.9' wide. Sold as-is.

Welcome home! This beautifully remodeled home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, NEW 8x14 storage shed, NEW FURNACE, NEW HEAT PUMP/AC!! All new floors throughout, as well as new countertops and painted interior. New high-end blinds throughout the whole home will also be installed prior to closing. We can't wait to welcome you home!

Discover your ultimate Fidalgo Island retreat in this meticulously maintained single-level haven. Featuring 3 beds, 2.5 baths, and an open-concept layout, this home is designed for effortless living. Unwind in the expansive primary suite with its luxurious garden soaking tub and ensuite bath. The chef's kitchen is a culinary delight with ample storage and a raised island. Admire breathtaking Mount Baker views from the spacious bonus/game room. With an oversized 2-car garage, 3rd bay workshop complete with a 1/2bath, garden room, and additional attic storage. This home offers both convenience and charm just blocks from local parks, hiking trails, shopping and restaurants. Welcome to your oasis of comfort, style, and endless possibilities!

Wake up to breathtaking views every morning, perched on a hillside overlooking the water. With a rooftop deck offering panoramic vistas of the bay and nearby islands, every sunset becomes a masterpiece. Inside, the great room & kitchen boast 12-foot ceilings, creating a spacious & airy ambiance. Floor-to-ceiling windows flood most rooms with natural light, illuminating the exquisite travertine tile & Brazilian hardwood floors. Community perks abound, including access to the beach, an event venue, a boat ramp, & an athletic court. Embrace the coastal lifestyle as you kayak & beachcomb just steps away from your home. Welcome home to a life of serenity & excitement, where every moment is filled with the beauty of the Pacific Northwest.

Uncover abundant living space at this multi-level dwelling on a quiet cul de sac, conveniently located in the heart of Mount Vernon. Host memorable gatherings in the tranquil fenced backyard, two inviting patios perfect for alfresco entertaining. Embrace peace of mind w/ the durable cement planked siding & recent HVAC upgrade, complete w/ refreshing AC. Step inside to discover elegant Timborana wood floors, new carpet, a sophisticated formal dining area, & a luxurious main bath featuring a separate tub & shower. You'll appreciate the proximity to the Kulshan Trail & being within the Harriet-Rowley Elem. boundary! Welcome to your new lifestyle of unparalleled satisfaction & enjoyment.

Welcome to Brickyard Park a new 55+ community. This home is a 3 bed/1.75 bath split rambler plan built on the park adjacent to the walking trail. Open Great room has a gas fireplace & lots of windows. Kitchen has upgraded white cabinets, island, and a gas range. There is a spacious Dining room. Primary bath has tile floor and tile shower. This home has over $28K of upgrades including quartz countertops, carpet, doors, light fixtures, insulated garage walls/ceilings & comfort height toilets. Mini splits for heat/AC. Covered rear patio. Landscaped & fence backyard. The community has a clubhouse, 1 acre park, outdoor lawn area, pickleball court, corn hole & horseshoe pits.

Stunning mountain, valley, and sunset views from this charming Mount Vernon home with mother-in-law/rental opportunity! Enjoy the bright living room with inviting natural light and floor to ceiling stone fireplace surround, cozy kitchen with eating bar and pass through to the dining room, plus two bedrooms on the main level. The downstairs mother-in-law/rental unit has a separate entrance and features a light-filled open floor plan, large kitchen and entertaining space, floor to ceiling brick fireplace in the bedroom, and spacious walk-in closet. Mini-split units both up and downstairs for heat and A/C. Outside enjoy the deck and large fenced backyard w storage shed, firepit, raised flower beds, hot tub and detached garage.

Lovely home nestled in the picturesque beauty of Anacortes, where majestic views of Mt. Baker and tranquil Fidalgo Bay greet you each day. Step into a charming turn-of-the-century abode boasting elegant oak and fir floors, basking in the warmth of natural light. Enjoy the enchanting ambiance and timeless appeal, with a fenced backyard offering a serene retreat complete with a pergola and expansive deck, perfect for soaking in the surroundings. Embrace the joy of gardening with ample space to cultivate your green oasis. This idyllic haven promises a lifestyle of comfort, elegance, and serenity amidst nature's splendor.

Welcome home to this charming 3-bedroom rambler nestled on a private, fully fenced lot on a quiet dead end street. With a 1-car garage, shed with power, and gated backyard access, storage is abundant. Step inside to find a cozy retreat adorned with wood ceilings and exposed beams, complemented by a gas-burning stove for added warmth.
